summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 59E, Page 24-369 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Page 79 of Exhibit E-2 to the Comprehensive Zoning Ordinance, 86300) to correct a cartographical error regarding the shoreline environmental classification of certain property in Block 2 of Maynard's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle in the vicinity of South Court Street and Lake Washington Boulevard by changing the environmental classification from Conservancy Management (CM) to Urban - Residential (UR).
